export var QUERY_TOTAL_CONFIRMED_CASES_SCOTLAND = "

SELECT
  Value
FROM
  indicators
WHERE
  Country = 'Scotland'
  AND Indicator = 'ConfirmedCases'
ORDER BY Date DESC LIMIT 1

";
export var QUERY_DAILY_CHANGE_CONFIRMED_CASES_SCOTLAND = "
SELECT
  Value - COALESCE(
    LAG(Value) OVER (
      PARTITION BY Indicator
      ORDER BY
        Date
    ),
    0
  )
FROM
  indicators
WHERE
  Country = 'Scotland'
  AND Indicator = 'ConfirmedCases'
ORDER BY
  Date DESC
LIMIT 1
";
